      </section>
      <section class="" style="   box-sizing: border-box; " powered-by="xiumi.us">
        <section class="" style=" margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px;  box-sizing: border-box; ">
          <section class="" style="border: 5px solid rgb(87, 65, 65); padding: 10px; box-sizing: border-box; background-color: rgb(63, 59, 58);">
            <section class="" style="box-sizing: border-box;" powered-by="xiumi.us">
              <section class="" style="   box-sizing: border-box; ">
                <section class="" style="padding: 10px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box;">
                  <p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 14px;"> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;这两年，涨价似乎已成常态，不论你信与不信，物价上涨已是不争的事实，从身边的生活中可以感受出来。此外，房价也进入了涨价通道，而后又轮到商品期货暴涨，这一切好像大家都相互约好似的，你唱完戏我再上场。</span></p>
                  <section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><br style="box-sizing: border-box;">
                  </section>
                  <p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 14px;"><span style="color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(63, 59, 58);"> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span>虽然上周五期货市场迎来一轮大暴跌，期货种类大面积从涨停板突然直线暴跌，部分品种甚至打到了跌停，但本质上来说，市场是动态平衡的，没有涨又哪来的跌？众所周知，商品的价格是由供求关系决定的，供不应求的时候，商品会涨，但是供需平衡的时候，如果货币严重超发，他也会涨。所以这一轮的上涨，除了黑色系是由于供给侧改革引发可以用供需关系解释之外，其他的普通品种和货币供应量是有很大关系的。</span></p>
                  <p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
                  <p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 14px;"><span style="color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(63, 59, 58);"> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span>中国有二轮货币超发，2008年底是一轮大的，2015年中旬是一轮是小的。由于这一轮房价的上涨，15年中旬之后频繁降准降息所释放的大量货币，被房地产吸纳了进去，物价像钉子一样被钉死在了地上。如果房地产被打压，货币溢出，那么各地生活用品的价格就纷纷暴涨。</span></p>
                </section>
              </section>
            </section>
          </section>
        </section>
      </section>
      <section class="" style="   box-sizing: border-box; " powered-by="xiumi.us">
        <section class="" style=" margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; overflow: hidden;  box-sizing: border-box; ">
          <section class="" style="display: inline-block; box-sizing: border-box;">
            <section style="display: inline-block; vertical-align: top; width: 4em; height: 4em; border-radius: 50%; box-sizing: border-box; background-size: cover; background-position: 50% 50%; background-repeat: no-repeat;" class="">
              <section class="" style="width: 100%; height: 100%; overflow: hidden; box-sizing: border-box;"><img style="opacity: 0; box-sizing: border-box; width: 100% !important; height: auto !important; visibility: visible !important;"  class="" data-type="png" data-ratio="1" data-w="80" _width="100%" src="<?php echo $filePath;?>fing29_2.jpg" data-fail="0"></section>
            </section>
            <section style="width: 100%; margin-left: 1.2em; margin-top: -1.2em; box-sizing: border-box;">
              <section style="float: left; overflow: hidden; display: inline-block; vertical-align: middle; height: 2em; margin-left: 1em; border-bottom-left-radius: 1em; border-left-width: 1px; border-left-style: solid; border-left-color: rgb(87, 65, 65); border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: rgb(87, 65, 65); box-sizing: border-box; max-width: 85% !important;">
                <section class="" style="margin-left: 1.5em; line-height: 1.5; padding-right: 0.5em; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(87, 65, 65); box-sizing: border-box;">
                  <section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">板块上涨的轮动有一定规律</strong><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"></strong></span></section>
                </section>
              </section>
              <section style="float: left; width: 5%; margin-left: -1px; box-sizing: border-box;">
                <section style="width: 6px; height: 6px; margin-top: 1.82em; border-radius: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; background-color: rgb(87, 65, 65);"></section>
