      <section class="" style="   box-sizing: border-box; " powered-by="xiumi.us">
        <section class="" style="   box-sizing: border-box; ">
          <section class="" style="font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box;">
            <p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span>如果你被2015年的股灾套住了，如果你错过了2015年房价的疯涨行情，如果你错过了2016年的期货暴涨行情，也许这时你已经开始盲目了，貌似这么多涨价的风潮总与你无关，到底又该如何乘上这一片涨价的东风，骑上那只风口上的“猪”呢？</span></p>
            <p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
            <p style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span>对于投资来说，我们一再强调，技术不重要，理念永远为先。正如道家所说，无道有术则无为。特别是在投资中，往往理论比技术重要的多，你眼光对了，把握了趋势，那么盈利只是迟早的事。当前局面下如何投资，还是先要回到当前的中国经济形势。08年放出去的大量货币没有收回，15年又放了一批，A股没有大规模赚钱效应，房地产遭到打压，资金无处可去，物价不暴涨那是不可能的，前天是螺纹钢，今天就是动力煤，明天是棉花，后天就是大蒜，大后天就是你家门口的早餐店。</span></p>
          </section>
        </section>
      </section>
      <section class="" style="   box-sizing: border-box; " powered-by="xiumi.us">
        <section class="" style=" margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em;  box-sizing: border-box; ">
          <section style="border-top-style: dashed; border-top-width: 5px; border-top-color: rgb(87, 65, 65); box-sizing: border-box;" class=""></section>
        </section>
      </section>
      <section class="" style="   box-sizing: border-box; " powered-by="xiumi.us">
        <section class="" style=" text-align: center; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px;  box-sizing: border-box; "><img src="<?php echo $filePath;?>fing29_4.jpg" style="display: block; margin:0 auto; max-width:500px;"/></section>
      </section>
      <section class="" style="   box-sizing: border-box; " powered-by="xiumi.us">
        <section class="" style=" margin-right: 0%; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0%; transform: translate3d(0px, 0px, 0px);  box-sizing: border-box; ">
          <section style="display: inline-block; width: 100%; vertical-align: top; padding-left: 20px; box-sizing: border-box; background-image: url(http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/9icMB0KOwxLsNrdkBSkNJnQqu7jgMnKQtJrzibJ6RliaL04pdS8wiaUgML2fpZ5hdPVKXYNn5nOn7pQJkpxMS8wHYQ/0?wx_fmt=png); background-attachment: scroll; background-size: 100%; background-position: 0% 0%; background-repeat: repeat;" class="">
            <section class="" style="   box-sizing: border-box; " powered-by="xiumi.us">
              <section class="" style="   box-sizing: border-box; ">
                <section class="" style="color: rgb(87, 65, 65); box-sizing: border-box;">
                  <section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">要解决这个问题，以下分析几个方案：</strong></span></section>
                </section>
