      </section>
      <section class="" style="   box-sizing: border-box; " powered-by="xiumi.us">
        <section class="" style="display: inline-block; width: 100%; border: 1px solid rgb(87, 65, 65); padding: 10px; box-sizing: border-box;">
          <section class="" style="box-sizing: border-box;" powered-by="xiumi.us">
            <section class="" style="   box-sizing: border-box; ">
              <section class="" style="font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box;">
                <section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14px; text-decoration: none;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14px; text-decoration: none; color: rgb(87, 65, 65); line-height: 28px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></strong></span><span style="font-size: 14px;"><span style="text-decoration: underline; box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="color: rgb(87, 65, 65); box-sizing: border-box;">1、收回货币，开始量化紧缩。</span></strong></span>这一点估计不可能，外国人都在拼命印钞票，中国断然不可能自己先收回钞票，那样的话，你等同于一个人承受了全球国家的损失，其他国家脱离危机，因为你替别人抗完了全部损失，就算国家要量化紧缩收回货币，那也是等美国先加息之后。</span></section>
                <section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">&nbsp;</span></section>
                <section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration: none;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="font-size: 16px; box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration: none; color: rgb(87, 65, 65); white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; </span></strong></span><span style="font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-size: 14px; text-decoration: underline; box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="font-size: 14px; color: rgb(87, 65, 65); box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">&nbsp;</span>2、重启房地产。</span></strong></span> 10月份中央刚刚下令调控房地产，朝令夕改也基本不可能，那也是一二年之后，才一二个月就改方向，那以后中央的政策谁还会信。</span></section>
                <section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">&nbsp;</span></section>
                <section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration: none;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="font-size: 16px; box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration: none; color: rgb(87, 65, 65); white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></strong></span><span style="font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-size: 14px; text-decoration: underline; box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="font-size: 14px; color: rgb(87, 65, 65); box-sizing: border-box;">3、大幅度供应产品，利用供需关系打压价格。</span></strong></span>这一点可以说难度比上述二个合起来还要大，毕竟商品并不能随心所欲的制造出来。</span></section>
                <section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">&nbsp;</span></section>
                <section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration: none;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="font-size: 16px; box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration: none; color: rgb(87, 65, 65); white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; </span></strong></span><span style="font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-size: 14px; text-decoration: underline; box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="font-size: 14px; color: rgb(87, 65, 65); box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">&nbsp;</span>4、让工业品及原材料涨价。</span></strong></span>这一点也很困难，因为工业品价格的上涨所滋生的泡沫，一旦爆炸更危险，工业品暴跌对工业体系的伤害之大足以动摇国本，因此这条路行不通。</span></section>
                <section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">&nbsp;</span></section>
                <section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration: none;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="font-size: 16px; box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration: none; color: rgb(87, 65, 65); white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; </span></strong></span><span style="font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-size: 14px; text-decoration: underline; box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="font-size: 14px; color: rgb(87, 65, 65); box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">&nbsp;</span>5、启动股市，利用A股的赚钱效应锁住并吸引资金。</span></strong></span>股市的容量之大完全可以吸收足够多的资金，但必须得考虑一点，就是股市的流动性太好，也就意味着变动性太大，不像房地产那么好控制，即便启动股市只能压制几个月到半年的物价，也可以缓冲一下，这个方案有可能性，但是概率并不是必然。</span></section>
                <section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">&nbsp;</span></section>
                <section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14px; text-decoration: none;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14px; text-decoration: none; color: rgb(87, 65, 65); line-height: 28px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; </span></strong></span><span style="text-decoration: underline; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14px;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="text-decoration: underline; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(87, 65, 65);"><span style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">&nbsp;</span>6、让居民忍受1至2年物价飞涨，随后再次启动房地产，然后又可以缓和1至2年，拖到中国经济好转，逐步收回多余的货币，让平民来承受改革转型的阵痛。</span></strong></span></section>
              </section>
            </section>
          </section>
